title: [Karazja Jungle, Lost Garden]
description: Although the jungle has inexorably overgrown this small area, it is still possible to discern it was once a formal garden.  A fountain stands to one side, the water in the basin filthy and stagnant.  The thorny runners of rose bushes have pulled down a rusted metal trellis.  A grey marble bench has been tipped over and damaged by some heavy object.
paths: Obvious paths: east, south, west, northwest
